OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisney boss calls for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers to return to office
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disney's boss has called on employees  
OL,6, who are currently working from home to 
OL,7, start going into the office for four   
OL,8, days a week from the start of March.   
OL,10,FChief executive Bob Iger said so-called
OL,11,F"hybrid" workers will now be asked to  
OL,12,Ftreat "Monday through Thursday as      
OL,13,Fin-person workdays".                   
OL,15,FHe also highlighted his view that      
OL,16,Fface-to-face collaboration is key to "a
OL,17,Fcreative business like ours".          
OL,19,FThe announcement comes two months after
OL,20,FMr Iger's shock return to Disney.      
